title: DENIM DOMINATORS: The Extraordinary Story of Blue Delta Jeans, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO302
itunes:title: DENIM DOMINATORS: The Extraordinary Story of Blue Delta Jeans, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO302
description: What can you learn about business from two guys from Tupelo, Mississippi? A lot. Josh West & Nick Weaver are two of the most incredible entrepreneurs I’ve met in a long time! They were best friends as kids & are now the founders of Blue Delta Jeans, a company that makes the best blue jeans I've ever worn in my life! We talked about their story, their struggle, & the lessons every entrepreneur can apply. You're not just going to learn a lot in this episode. You're going to laugh, too. A lot.
